                  "revisionId": 2663914,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "For any non-integer magazine values the magazine size is simply rounded to the nearest whole number. For example, a Strun modded with a max rank Burdened Magazine will have a calculated magazine size of 6 × (1 + 60%) = 9.6 , which will simply round to 10 ."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Burdened Magazine",
                  "pageId": 233713,
                  "revisionId": 2663914,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Suitable for shotguns with innately high magazine capacities ( Boar , Boar Prime , Sobek , or Phage )."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Burdened Magazine",
                  "pageId": 233713,
                  "revisionId": 2663914,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Could make one magazine last entire fights without needing any reloads, thus nullifying the negative reload speed."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
