                  "revisionId": 2663914,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Combining this mod and Ammo Stock would give +120% magazine size to the modded shotgun."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Burdened Magazine",
                  "pageId": 233713,
                  "revisionId": 2663914,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Unlike Tainted Mag and Tainted Clip , this mod increases the magazine size just as much as the non-corrupt counterpart, hence it should only be used in conjunction with Ammo Stock in builds aiming to maximize magazine size."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Burdened Magazine",
                  "pageId": 233713,
                  "revisionId": 2663914,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "With this mod and Ammo Stock, Tigris and it's variants can reach a magazine size of 4. With a rank 5 Ammo Stock, Burdened Magazine can be left at rank 1 to minimize the reload penalty and capacity drain."
                }
